               <msContents>
                  <summary>The Ms. contains the following texts:
 I) Maṣḥafa ʾaslǝṭi, Lectionary
                     for the entire year (fols. 3ra-34vb)
 II) Excerpt from a liturgical book
                     (Maṣḥafa qǝddase “Missal”, or Maṣḥafa gǝṣṣawe [?]) (fols. 34ra-38vb)
 
                     Additiones 1-2.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Cp. Mss.<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESams011">AMS-011</ref>, S<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdgm007">DGM-007</ref>,<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESgms015">GMS-015</ref>,<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdmd021">DMD-021</ref>.</note>
                  </msItem>
